div(class="relative min-h-full overflow-hidden bg-zinc-950 text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50")
    div(class="absolute inset-0 bg-cover bg-center", style="background-image: url('/assets/bg-login.optimized.webp')")
    div(class="absolute inset-0 bg-zinc-950/60")

    div(class="relative mx-auto flex min-h-screen max-w-6xl items-center px-5 py-8")
        div(class="grid w-full grid-cols-1 gap-6 lg:grid-cols-[minmax(0,1fr)_420px] lg:items-center")
            section(class="hidden min-h-[500px] flex-col justify-between text-white lg:flex")
                div
                    div(class="flex items-center gap-3")
                        div(*ngIf="!hasLogo()", class="flex h-11 w-11 items-center justify-center rounded-md bg-white text-sm font-black text-zinc-950") DI
                        div(*ngIf="hasLogo()", class="flex h-11 w-11 items-center justify-center overflow-hidden rounded-md bg-white")
                            img([src]="appearance.logo_url", [alt]="title()", class="h-full w-full object-contain")
                        div
                            p(class="text-base font-semibold") {{title()}}
                            p(class="text-sm text-zinc-300") 인프라 운영 콘솔
                    div(class="mt-12 max-w-xl")
                        h1(class="text-4xl font-semibold leading-tight") 서버와 서비스를 빠르게 점검합니다.
                        p(class="mt-4 max-w-lg text-base leading-7 text-zinc-200") 배포 상태, DDNS 도메인, 백업 이력, 작업 로그를 한 화면에서 확인하고 필요한 조치를 실행합니다.
                div(class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-3")
                    div(class="rounded-md border border-white/15 bg-white/10 px-3 py-3 backdrop-blur")
                        i(class="fa-solid fa-chart-line text-sm text-sky-200")
                        p(class="mt-2 text-sm font-semibold") 서버 상태
                        p(class="mt-1 text-xs leading-5 text-zinc-300") 자원 추이와 컨테이너 확인
                    div(class="rounded-md border border-white/15 bg-white/10 px-3 py-3 backdrop-blur")
                        i(class="fa-solid fa-layer-group text-sm text-emerald-200")
                        p(class="mt-2 text-sm font-semibold") 서비스 배포
                        p(class="mt-1 text-xs leading-5 text-zinc-300") Compose, 이미지, 롤백 관리
                    div(class="rounded-md border border-white/15 bg-white/10 px-3 py-3 backdrop-blur")
                        i(class="fa-solid fa-globe text-sm text-amber-200")
                        p(class="mt-2 text-sm font-semibold") DDNS / SSL
                        p(class="mt-1 text-xs leading-5 text-zinc-300") 도메인 연결과 인증서 점검
                    div(class="rounded-md border border-white/15 bg-white/10 px-3 py-3 backdrop-blur")
                        i(class="fa-solid fa-clock-rotate-left text-sm text-violet-200")
                        p(class="mt-2 text-sm font-semibold") 작업 추적
                        p(class="mt-1 text-xs leading-5 text-zinc-300") 배포, 백업, 매크로 이력

            section(class="rounded-md border border-white/20 bg-white/95 p-5 shadow-xl backdrop-blur dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-950/95 md:p-6")
                div(class="mb-6 flex items-center gap-3 lg:hidden")
                    div(*ngIf="!hasLogo()", class="flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-md bg-zinc-950 text-sm font-black text-white dark:bg-zinc-100 dark:text-zinc-950") DI
                    div(*ngIf="hasLogo()", class="flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center overflow-hidden rounded-md bg-white")
                        img([src]="appearance.logo_url", [alt]="title()", class="h-full w-full object-contain")
                    div
                        p(class="text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") {{title()}}
                        p(class="text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 인프라 운영 콘솔

                div(*ngIf="loading()", class="rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-white p-10 text-center text-sm text-zinc-500 dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-400") 정보를 불러오는 중입니다.

                div(*ngIf="!loading() && requiresSetup()", class="space-y-5")
                    div(class="flex items-start justify-between gap-4")
                        div
                            h2(class="text-xl font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") 설치 관리자 필요
                            p(class="mt-1 text-sm text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") {{setupStatusMessage()}}
                        span(class="inline-flex rounded-md border border-amber-200 bg-amber-50 px-2.5 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-amber-700 dark:border-amber-900/70 dark:bg-amber-950/40 dark:text-amber-300") {{setupStatusLabel()}}

                    div(class="rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-zinc-50 px-4 py-3 dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-900")
                        p(class="text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") Installer URL
                        p(class="mt-1 break-all text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") {{installerUrl()}}

                    button(type="button", data-testid="installer-open", (click)="openInstaller()", class="inline-flex h-10 w-full items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-md bg-zinc-950 px-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white hover:bg-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-100 dark:text-zinc-950 dark:hover:bg-zinc-200")
                        i(class="fa-solid fa-screwdriver-wrench")
                        span 설치 관리자 열기

                div(*ngIf="!loading() && !requiresSetup()", class="space-y-5")
                    div
                        h2(class="text-xl font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") 운영자 로그인
                        p(class="mt-1 text-sm text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 운영 콘솔 비밀번호를 입력하세요.

                    label(class="block")
                        span(class="mb-1 block text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 비밀번호
                        input(type="password", autocomplete="current-password", aria-label="비밀번호", data-testid="password-input", [(ngModel)]="data.password", (keyup.enter)="login()", class="h-10 w-full rounded-md border border-zinc-300 bg-white px-3 text-sm text-zinc-900 placeholder:text-zinc-400 focus:border-zinc-500 focus:outline-none focus:ring-1 focus:ring-zinc-500 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:bg-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-100")

                    button(type="button", data-testid="login-submit", (click)="login()", class="inline-flex h-10 w-full items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-md bg-zinc-950 px-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white hover:bg-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-100 dark:text-zinc-950 dark:hover:bg-zinc-200")
                        i(class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right-to-bracket")
                        span 로그인
